markupSmallText: Added to actual spend and reflected in client reporting
ttImpressions: Number of times the ad was shown
ttClicks: Number of times the ad was clicked
ttConversions: Number of times the ad achieved the outcome, based on the objective and settings
ttClientSpends: Amount of money spent on ads
ttAvgCPC: Average of total cost divided by number of clicks
ttCostPerConv: Total cost value divided by number of conversions
ttConvRate: Total conversions divided by number of ad interactions
toIntegrateYourAccount: to integrate your google account and select the google ads client id for which you want to see the data.
toIntegrateYourFBAccount: to integrate your Facebook account and select the Facebook Ad Account-ID for which you want to see the data.
toUseGoogleAdReporting: To use Google Ads reporting, you must reconnect your Google Ads manager account.
toGoToIntegrations: to go to the integrations page.
toUseFBAdReporting: In order to use the Facebook Ads Reporting, you need to disconnect and reconnect your Facebook account.
